            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前 Vitalik Buterin 在去中心化社交協議 <a href="https://warpcast.com/vitalik.eth" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Farcaster</a> 接受羣眾提問，他談到對以太坊未來的擔憂，其中與 AI 大有關聯。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/vitalik-on-ethereum-future-concern#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65311dc88351d"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
