            <title>
                <![CDATA[Aptos 停機！超過 4 小時沒出塊，目前已恢復]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>根據 <a href="https://aptoscan.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AptoScan</a> 數據，Move 語系公鏈 Aptos 已超過 4 個小時沒有產出新的區塊，目前尚未釐清原因為何。</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-81092 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-10-19-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.56.08.png?resize=1126%2C317&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1126" height="317" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-19-上午 11.56.08.png?w=1126&amp;ssl=1 1126w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-19-上午 11.56.08.png?resize=300%2C84&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-19-上午 11.56.08.png?resize=1024%2C288&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-19-上午 11.56.08.png?resize=600%2C169&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-19-上午 11.56.08.png?resize=768%2C216&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>關於此現象，Aptos 官方於今晨表示網路上的交易已受影響，仍還積極解決問題中。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Your energy for Aptos One was so electric, you cut the lights!</p><p>What that means at the moment is that transactions on the network have been impacted. We are working diligently to resolve the issue and will keep you updated upon completion.</p><p>— Aptos (@Aptos_Network) <a href="https://twitter.com/Aptos_Network/status/1714799744231539064?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 19, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2>Aptos 已恢復運行 (10/19 中午 12:30 更新)</h2><p>在經過近 5 小時的停機後，Aptos 目前已恢復運作，實際停機原因為何還有待官方説明。</p>
